                            skos:definition "an owl:ObjectProperty relating an ec:Annotation to an ec:MediaResource"@en .


###  http://www.ebu.ch/metadata/ontologies/ebucoreplus#isAttributedTo
ec:isAttributedTo rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
