                   skos:definition "an owl:ObjectProperty relating an ec:EditorialObject to an ec:PublicationService"@en .


###  http://www.ebu.ch/metadata/ontologies/ebucoreplus#isDubOf
ec:isDubOf rdf:type owl:ObjectProperty ;
